    <name>Multiple Means of Action &amp; Expression​</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/udl-brain-actionandexpression-outline.png" alt="" width="150" height="120" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_right"&gt;&lt;ul role="list"&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="1" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b530670c-828e-403c-836c-19bd30f517c1}{221}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Celebrate the different ways&amp;nbsp;learners can share what they&amp;nbsp;know or have&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;learned, make sure to highlight experiential knowledge and non-traditional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;strategies like&amp;nbsp;storytelling, interviews with family members, biographies, etc.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="2" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b530670c-828e-403c-836c-19bd30f517c1}{224}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Provide opportunities for&amp;nbsp;collaboration and sharing of the teaching space,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;by having learners teach one another &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="3" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b530670c-828e-403c-836c-19bd30f517c1}{227}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Provide examples of revisions from professionals, peers and former&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;classmates, as a strategy for changing&amp;nbsp;students’ negative&amp;nbsp;thought processes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;when&amp;nbsp;they encounter learning&amp;nbsp;challenges&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="4" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b530670c-828e-403c-836c-19bd30f517c1}{230}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Showcase growth by building in periodic&amp;nbsp;self-reflections and asking learners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to reflect on and&amp;nbsp;share with others how far they have come&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider-wave-1.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
